headline: Smurfit Westrock Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: DUBLIN, February 03, 2026-- Smurfit Westrock plc (NYSE:SW, LSE:SWR) (the "Company") announced today that its Board approved a quarterly dividend of $0.4523 per share on its ordinary shares. The quarterly dividend of $0.4523 per ordinary share is payable March 18, 2026 to shareholders of record at the close of business on February 17, 2026.
